FeedPackage.Description: Multi-tenant MVC and WebApi application foundation with management for sites, users, roles, and geographic data. Typically you should not install this directly but instead install the package cloudscribe.Core.Web.Integration which will also install cloudscribe.Web.Core along with the integration code needed to wire it up in your empty web application project. You are allowed to modify the integration code after it is added to your project.
